snippet.title: Heritage vs Gibson Lawsuit, Travel Plans Cancelled, New Fender Mustang GTX  - ITB Podcast
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching the intheblues tone podcast! I hope everyone is staying positive in this tough time with everything that is going on around the world.  I hope you enjoy this episode. This episode we take a look at the Heritage vs Gibson lawsuit, the new Fender Mustang GTX amplifiers, and much more!

Time Codes:
My YouTube Trip to the USA Cancelled - 0:00
Heritage vs Gibson - Another Lawsuit! - 5:20 
 - Read the article here: https://bit.ly/2U7fiX0
 - Check out the new Heritage Guitars: imp.i114863.net/Heritage (Sweetwater affiliate link)
The Great Guitar Purge of 2020 Update - 9:57
Fender Mustang GTX Amplifiers - 16:11
 - Check it out on Sweetwater: imp.i114863.net/GTX (in stock/affiliate link)
My Top 3 Solid-State Amplifiers ever - 20:10
